data.text:
Company Profile

Founded in 2003, Xinxing Label has grown into a premier national high-tech enterprise, specializing in self-adhesive label printing and offering a full spectrum of services, including design, printing, and die-cutting. Catering to a wide array of industries such as food and beverage, textiles, electronics, healthcare, and logistics, our products are celebrated nationwide and across the globe. With exports reaching the United States, Japan, South Korea, Germany, the UK, France, Italy, Australia, Mexico, and beyond, our commitment to excellence and versatility sets us apart, underscoring our role as a trusted partner in diverse market sectors.

Our Label Products

Xinxing Label specializes in the expert design and printing of versatile self-adhesive labels, essential for industries like food and beverage, fashion and textiles, electronics, healthcare, and warehousing. Our expertise ensures high-quality, reliable labels for diverse applications, enhancing brand visibility and product functionality.

Our Advantage
